Package test

package test
Provides classes for testing the application.

Includes unit tests for the calculator, shipping rule and shipping rule loader classes as well as random based tests for the calculator class.

Contains the following test classes:

  • CalculatorTest - Unit tests for the calculator class
  • ShippingRuleTest - Unit tests for the shipping rule class
  • ShippingRuleLoaderTest - Unit tests for the shipping rule loader class
  • ErrorDisplayStateTest - Unit tests for the error display state enum
  • SettingsManagerTest - Unit tests for the settings manager class
  • CurrencyTest - Unit tests for the currency enum
  • MeasurementSystemTest - Unit tests for the measurement system enum
  • CalculatorRandomTest - Random based tests for the calculator class
